rows.label: qev060506_MSG0032
rows.name:
I'll try to find an emergency hire to help out while
you're looking for that everfreeze ore or jagitos copper.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0033
rows.name:
You said the Zaruboggan, right?
Gotta admit I'm not super jazzed to talk to them
through those freaky masks...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0034
rows.name:
But I'll do my best! And who knows?
Maybe I'll uncover a waste-management genius.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0084
rows.name:
Welcome back to ground zero!
So how's that everfreeze ore or jagitos copper
coming along...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0086
rows.name: Not ready yet? Okay! Well, try to hurry, yeah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0087
rows.name: In the meantime, I'll get busy scouting us a savior.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0039
rows.name:
Ah, perfect! Did you get the everfreeze ore?
Or jagitos copper? They won't fix the problem,
but they'll make it a lot better...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0040
rows.name:
WHOA that's cold! But yeah, okay, great.
This should bring down the temperature on the unit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0041
rows.name: Thanks! Oh, and bonus thanks for the advice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0042
rows.name:
I scouted some Zaruboggan like you said, and as soon
as they turned up, they zapped all of the contaminants
out of the air![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0043
rows.name:
Smoke used to be billowing out like gangbusters,
but it should be returning to normal soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0044
rows.name:
Arsenican and Trachlo are amazing! Aren't you guys?
Honestly, they're like garbage wizards.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0045
rows.name:
Ah, you are the BLADE I met previously. *fsssh*
I did not know you were acquainted with Liza.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0046
rows.name:
I was given the opportunity to devoltanize some
exceptionally nice voltant here. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0047
rows.name:
It has been a long while since I felt so sated. *fsssh*
This place is akin to Golbogga's garden of bountyâ€”
our homeworld of Bedun.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0048
rows.name:
I have no idea what you're talking about,
but it sounds great![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_JNK0060
rows.name: Concur

rows.label: qev060506_SEL0061
rows.name: Agree that there's no need to sweat the details.

rows.label: qev060506_JNK0070
rows.name: Teach

rows.label: qev060506_SEL0071
rows.name: Give Liza a thorough lesson in Zaruboggan lingo.

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0049
rows.name:
I love that you don't care either. Because really, what's
worrying about it going to get us? Wrinkles and grays![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0050
rows.name:
GAAAH! If you don't stop right now, I'm going to
Golbogga your voltant right in the Zaruboggan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0051
rows.name: Sorry, but...I can't. I just can't...take...any more...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0052
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0053
rows.name:
Okay, I've decided to give up ever understanding
your weird jargon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0054
rows.name:
But seriously, thanks for everything.
From me, but also...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0055
rows.name:
Hello. I'm Dazbeno? Technical advisor for this place?
Yes, well, I would like you to to to have this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0056
rows.name:
Even with a full arsenal of Ma-non tech, I couldn't
have made all this clean, you know? But then the
Zaruboggan came in and and just did it somehow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0057
rows.name:
Yeah, what he said! You and those Zaruboggan
saved this place AND the city![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060506_MSG0058
rows.name: And I didn't get yeeelled aaat! Ha ha ha wheee![ST:wait ]
